{"prayers":[{"phelps":"AB02304TST","text":"Nu vo ada han e cuda e Tanawa Tanawa e wap pie-it nush ta Weed cada my a too Wee a Ma tu queet me quash  me quash cada e auta quan eada we how ta quan Kaden ought to quan qua e hoeta quan sa Wee e whan e cua Cada oo we qad me on ich, e Wab wut e Na did quay, e New casa e wa nu in.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\n* There is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","category":"Mono","order_in_cat":1,"source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"246ca368-d0c6-4372-b545-7bd86aee1c68","v":"25mpi0x2g23pyjbpg0c957nmw","book":"nai-US:bpnet","book_cats":{"ar:bpapp":{"cat":"النوروز","cat_order":23,"order_in_cat":2},"ar:bpnet":{"cat":"النيروز","order_in_cat":4},"bn:bpnet":{"cat":"মহান বা’ব-এর জন্মদিনের ফলকলিপি","order_in_cat":1},"bs:bpnet":{"cat":"Duhovno Vijeće","order_in_cat":1},"cy:bpnet":{"cat":"Dawn","order_in_cat":1},"de:bpnet":{"cat":"Das mittlere Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"en:bpnet":{"cat":"Birth of The Báb","order_in_cat":2},"eu:bpnet":{"cat":"Gorespen Jainkoari","order_in_cat":3},"fa:bpnet":{"cat":"الواح ایام صیام","order_in_cat":2},"ht:bpnet":{"cat":"Priyè pou Fanm","order_in_cat":2},"id:bpnet":{"cat":"Loh Perayaan Kelahiran Sang Bab","order_in_cat":1},"is:bpnet":{"cat":"Lofgjörð og þökk","order_in_cat":7},"kl:bpnet":{"cat":"Aalajaassuseq","order_in_cat":1},"lg:bpnet":{"cat":"OKUSONYIYIBWA","order_in_cat":1},"lt:bpnet":{"cat":"Išbandymai ir sunkumai","order_in_cat":3},"ml:bpnet":{"cat":"പ്രബോധനം","order_in_cat":7},"nai-US:bpnet":{"cat":"Mono","order_in_cat":1},"nl:bpapp":{"cat":"Lof en dankbaarheid","cat_order":17,"order_in_cat":6},"nl:bpnet":{"cat":"Lof en dankbaarheid","order_in_cat":6},"no:bpnet":{"cat":"Besøkelsens tavle","order_in_cat":1},"pl:bpnet":{"cat":"Ornamenty","order_in_cat":1},"ro:bpnet":{"cat":"Zilele Intercalare","order_in_cat":